OL,3,CPassenger whose necklace was stolen
OL,4,Csays bus driver 'didn't deserve'
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FA passenger who had their necklace
OL,8,Fstolen on a bus has said the bus
OL,9,Fdriver who retrieved it "didn't
OL,10,Fdeserve" to be sacked.
OL,12,FMark Hehir, 62, was fired by Metroline
OL,13,Fafter he chased down a thief who had
OL,14,Fstolen the jewellery belonging to one
OL,15,Fof his passengers, Katalin Kaszas.
OL,17,FMs Kaszas, 46, said that she felt "so
OL,18,Fguilty" after learning Mr Hehir had
OL,19,Flost his job as a result of
OL,20,Fconfronting the thief.
