OL,7,FShe told the Press Association: "I
OL,8,Fthink it was unjust. I don't think he
OL,9,Fdeserved that. If he doesn't do what
OL,10,Fhe did, anything could have happened
OL,11,Fto me."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Justice Secretary David
OL,14,FLammy told the House of Commons on
OL,15,FTuesday that Mr Hehir "is of course a
OL,16,Fhero and deserves our support".
OL,18,FHe added: "I'm following this case
OL,19,Fvery closely."
