OL,7,FMore than 125,000 people have signed a
OL,8,Fpetition in support Mr Hehir, which
OL,9,Fwas launched after an employment
OL,10,Ftribunal upheld Metroline's decision
OL,11,Fto sack the bus driver, a ruling first
OL,12,Freported by PA.
OL,14,FIn another sign of public support for
OL,15,Fthe former bus driver, a GoFundMe page
OL,16,Ffor Mr Hehir has raised more than
OL,17,F#28,000.
