OL,7,FEarlier on Tuesday, Mr Hehir ` who is
OL,8,Foriginally from Limerick in Ireland,
OL,9,Fbut now lives in north-west London `
OL,10,Fwas invited into parliament by shadow
OL,11,Fjustice minister Kieran Mullan.
OL,13,FMr Mullan told PA: "I think Metroline
OL,14,Fneed to come out and apologise, Mark
OL,15,Fdeserves an apology, it's quite clear
OL,16,Fthey've gotten this wrong".
OL,18,FOn June 25 2024, Mr Hehir was driving
OL,19,Fthe 206 bus, which runs between
OL,20,FWembley and Maida Vale in north-west
OL,21,FLondon.
