OL,4,Csays bus driver 'didn't deserve'
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FAfter passing Harlesden High Street, a
OL,8,Fman on board the bus pushed past a
OL,9,Ffemale passenger snatching a necklace
OL,10,Ffrom around her neck and ran off.
OL,12,FMr Hehir chased after the man down the
OL,13,Fstreet and returned the necklace to
OL,14,Fthe female passenger.
OL,16,FThe man then reappeared, walking
OL,17,Ftowards the bus, where he threw "the
OL,18,Ffirst punch" at Mr Hehir, a tribunal
OL,19,Fwas told.
OL,26,@yD@aOUzD@LO]
