OL,7,FThe bus driver then responded in self-
OL,8,Fdefence and hit the man once, knocking
OL,9,Fhim unconscious.
OL,11,FMr Hehir then restrained the man on
OL,12,Fthe pavement for almost "half an hour"
OL,13,Funtil police arrived.
OL,15,FThe men were both arrested, however Mr
OL,16,FHehir was subsequently released and
OL,17,Ftold he would face no further police
OL,18,Faction.
