OL,7,FA police case review said "the
OL,8,Fclaimant had used force which was
OL,9,Fproportionate and necessary in the
OL,10,Fcircumstances in the defence of
OL,11,Fhimself and the female passenger".
OL,13,FA Metroline spokesperson said: "The
OL,14,Ftribunal has upheld the dismissal as
OL,15,Ffair."
